{
  "stem": "26111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wasn't-- so I can't really say what the scene was, but it was obviously, openly or controlledly, it was a very emotional scene before the train finally steamed away.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, we went into a train that had some young people, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] adults, that were Jewish, and that would take care of us, look after us, till we got where we were going.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- but they were authority figures, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were not really close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They sort of told us where to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, of course, there were the guards, the train guards, which had the, the-- they didn't have the SS uniform.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That didn't come into play until the border station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there it did come into play, quite brutally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Inklings aren't thoughts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they are.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they are, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It goes up and down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hope goes up and down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Until the war, I was in regular correspondence with them through the regular mail.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that, it became much more-- much more rare and much more limited, our communication.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But during the war-- or during the, the period before the war, after my departure, before the outbreak of war, they were doing their best to talk to me about-- write to me about the little things of life, about the way that things were, toning down the bad things, playing up the pleasant things-- and always imbued with this hope and giving reports on what, what, what they were pursuing-- what route they were pursuing for immigration.",
      "word_count": 78
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so there was always an element of hope.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that doesn't mean that I was thinking at all times that that would succeed.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
